---
title: Greek-Style Chicken & Lemon Pepper Fries with Garden Salad & Tzatziki
description: Garlicky and tender Greek chicken strips are topped off with this incredibly refreshing tzatziki and side of herbed fries. With a crisp cos salad to finish, you won't know which bit to eat first!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/greek-style-chicken-lemon-pepper-fries-24151c5a.jpg
